data.description: Welcome to this charming 4-bedroom, 4-bathroom single-family home in North Hall County. With 3,475 square feet of living space, this residence offers a blend of comfort, elegance, and functionality. Spacious Layout: The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating an inviting space for family gatherings and entertaining. Gourmet Kitchen: The well-appointed kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample cabinet storage. The living room boasts a cozy fireplace, perfect for chilly evenings. Master Suite: Retreat to the master suite with its own private bath, walk-in closet, gas log fireplace and serene views. Outdoor Oasis: Step outside to the courtyard overlooking the lush backyard with fireplace, ideal for enjoying morning coffee or hosting summer barbecues. Additional Bedrooms: Three additional bedrooms provide flexibility for a home office, guest room, or playroom. Private Office/Den Community Amenities: Located in a premier North Hall subdivision with a pool and tennis courts. Storage: Tons of storage throughout, including a two-car garage. This is a family-friendly neighborhood in North Hall that offers a community association activity area with tennis courts and a pool for social events.  Year Built: 1993 Lot Size: Approximately 0.75 acres  Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home! Schedule a showing today.
